{"TopicId":164070,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Rocker-Bogie System","CreatedByName":"Casualnaut","CreatedById":178396,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-04T20:19:47Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Casualnaut","CreatedById":178396,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-04T20:19:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi folks, it is Casualnaut back with another suggestion for the glorious Squad development team.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was wondering if there could be an end-tier rover wheels that used the Rocker-Bogie System JPL uses on the Mars rovers. They would come in entire sets of 3 wheels, and would crawl up terrain like this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/55/Rocker_bogie.gif/220px-Rocker_bogie.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022220px-Rocker_bogie.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rocker-bogie#/media/File:Rocker_bogie.gif\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EImage provided by Wikipedia\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cem\u003ENote: I may edit the thread as responses come to make it the best suggestion possible.\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Grand Ship Builder","CreatedById":144766,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-04T21:19:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere could be, but I don\u0027t think Squad wants to add those... yet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the meantime, you can search for mods, or make your own.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fourfa","CreatedById":151713,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-04T21:40:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/157974-mars-rover-type-rocker-bogie-suspension-system-on-rover-bogie-mcbogeface/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nseems relevant\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Casualnaut","CreatedById":178396,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-05T19:12:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI play on console...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DunaManiac","CreatedById":176003,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-05T20:15:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223140890\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022164070\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221501960358\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022178396\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Casualnaut\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Casualnaut said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI play on console...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMe too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MiffedStarfish","CreatedById":175356,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-05T20:31:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you were really dedicated, you could make it with stock hinges and put loads of \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E on the main body, maybe set to radial out with a vertical control point.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-06T18:25:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223140890\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022164070\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp